{"tid":1745273,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"選舉造假；投白票；投黎都無用架啦","createTime":"2019-11-22T06:41:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-22T07:36:43.000Z","uid":37722,"like":7,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"9aa36c853c453544eb5361e0bc99b64033571eb1","tid":1745273,"uid":37722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T06:41:12.000Z","msg":"有人話選舉肯定造假而投白票，咁我用用簡單logic分析呢次選舉：<br />\n<br />\n假設大家都認同選舉肯定造假<br />\n<br />\n1. 你講造假，投白票：<br />\n建制贏，建制話無人想要民主，你就話選舉造假，大家繼續維持同溫層，我地輸<br />\n<br />\n2. 你講造假，但跟策略投非建制：<br />\n建制輸，建制無聲出，你高調同人講抗爭有民意基礎，繼續抗爭，對家無聲出，我地贏<br />\n<br />\n理大一役大家都認係輸得慘，連連儂場都比人清到無哂，我地急需一場勝仗調整返士氣，雖然輸左我唔會停，但輸左的確對我方影響士氣影響好大<br />\n<br />\n求下大家，我想贏一次呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6dd8a0d33d270510269b2024ca97effb067cc58b","tid":1745273,"uid":37722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T06:42:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"76fbbad057ddb29779d77e15b53733841a990b62","tid":1745273,"uid":37722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T06:43:16.000Z","msg":"推比所有投白票人睇"},{"pid":"072d5d059e4844acc5acae002a69ccccb54f9ab8","tid":1745273,"uid":37722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T06:44:41.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"36ba72e1f973ccc82862282b54732a9ff0643678","tid":1745273,"uid":123456,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T06:45:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">on9標題<br />\n拉</span>"},{"pid":"fd2af4c15c41a00b5a6a67e50a1af58422c6723f","tid":1745273,"uid":147520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T06:45:56.000Z","msg":"推一鑊"},{"pid":"cfd57bf61e25933ddf00a4e78100e5ca5694b667","tid":1745273,"uid":49336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T06:47:08.000Z","msg":"理大一役？ 見到順便貼埋先<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Sudk8Yv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSudk8Yv.png&h=43d976